 Finally, after thrilling us with the snippet to his new song with Simi on IG, Mr. Eazi releases “Doyin”, a classic record produced by Killertunes. This record is a love jam straight from the heart, it explains how both lovers are feeling and how badly they want each other around. This is the second time Mr. Eazi and Simi will be joining forces together after the magic they performed on the first ‘Surrender‘. “Doyin” is a follow up to ‘Supernova‘ which is still trending and on high demand. Once again their delivery is topnotch. Listen and Enjoy!   The post Mr Eazi – “Doyin” ft. Simi (Prod. by Killertunes) appeared first on tooXclusive. Source: TooXclusiv